    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good, well-maintained condition and is ready for its next owner. The exterior retains a strong shine, though upon close inspection, you will find a few minor stone chips on the hood and some light surface scratches consistent with regular use. Inside, the cabin is clean and comfortable, with only slight wear on the driver's seat bolster and floor mats. Mechanically, it runs smoothly and has been serviced regularly, though it may soon require standard maintenance items like new brake pads. Overall, it is a reliable and presentable car that offers great value for someone looking for a dependable daily driver.",
