      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my absolute pride and joy. This beauty is in truly incredible shape\u2014it honestly looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, and it's been garage-kept and pampered since day one. If you're looking for something that feels brand new without the brand-new price tag, you\u2019ve found it! Come take it for a spin, I promise you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 46500.0,
