    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a superlative 2004 Porsche 911 Carrera 4S, a widebody masterpiece preserved in showroom condition. This specimen features the M96.03 3.6L flat-six powerplant equipped with VarioCam Plus, delivering a seamless power band. The drivetrain is anchored by a Getrag G96/31 6-speed manual transaxle and a viscous-coupling all-wheel-drive system for peerless mechanical grip. Critically, the IMS bearing has been proactively retrofitted with a ceramic dual-row upgrade, and the rear main seal is bone dry. The chassis retains its factory-fresh rigidity, supported by Bilstein dampers and 18-inch hollow-spoke Turbo Twist alloys. Braking performance is handled by four-piston monoblock calipers over cross-drilled rotors with zero heat checking. A mechanically pristine, turn-key example for the discerning collector.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
